      "file_path": "openecomp-be/lib/openecomp-heat-lib/src/main/java/org/openecomp/sdc/heat/services/tree/HeatTreeManager.java",
      "patchset_number": 2,
      "line": 144,
      "message": "There's not much to do if you can't close the InputStream here. so try { fileContent.close() } catch (IOException ignored) { /* ignore */ } would be perfectly fine. Better yet, use the Java 7 try-with-resource construct: try (InputStream fileContent = ....) { ... }",
